Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model

Provides the classes and interfaces of the HOBO Direct Model API (see uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo for general description).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DArrayView<V>
    Common interface for both DArray and DArrayViewer.
    DCellView<V>
    Common interface for both DCell and DCellViewer.
    DFieldView<V>
    Common interface for both DField and DFieldViewer.
    DObject
    Interface implemented by all classes in the Object Model (OM).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DArray<V>
    Represents a multi-valued field in the Object Model (OM).
    DArrayViewer<V>
    Represents a view of a multi-valued field in the Object Model (OM).
    DCell<V>
    Represents a single-valued field in the Object Model (OM).
    DCellViewer<V>
    Represents a view of a single-valued field in the Object Model (OM).
    DConcept<D extends DObject>
    Type-safe representation of a concept-level frame within the Object Model (OM).
    DDisjunction<D extends DObject>
    Represents a disjunction of DObjects.
    DDisjunctionArray<D extends DObject>
    A DDisjunction-valued array bound to the same slot as a specific DObject-valued "source" array, enabling the setting of disjunction values for the slot.
    DDisjunctionCell<D extends DObject>
    A DDisjunction-valued cell bound to the same slot as a specific DObject-valued "source" cell, enabling the setting of disjunction values for the slot.
    DField<V>
    Represents a field in the Object Model (OM).
    DFieldViewer<V,F extends DField<V>>
    Represents a view of a field in the Object Model (OM).
    DIdentity
    Represents the identity for a frames-based entity derived from a particular class or field in the Object Model (OM).
    DModel
    Represents the HOBO direct model, which is an Object Model (OM) within which domain concepts are represented directly by domain-specific Java classes (OM classes).
    DNumberRange<N extends java.lang.Number>
    Represents a numeric range.
    DNumberRangeCell<N extends java.lang.Number>
    A DNumberRange-valued cell bound to the same slot as a specific Number-valued "source" cell, enabling the setting of numeric-range values for the slot.

Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model Description

Provides the classes and interfaces of the HOBO Direct Model API (see uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo for general description).

NOTE: This is a companion package to both the uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.modeller and uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor packages, with each of which which it shares circular dependencies at the implementation level, though not at the API level. See uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo for further details.
